reviews.text:
their ice cream flavors can be lots of fun, you can take it to a next level by ordering one of the cereal/marshmallow cones.
I ordered the caramel something ice cream, it was very sweet and sadly had a grainy texture that I didn't enjoy.
I'd come back to try a different flavor.
Wonderful shop, great range of ice cream and amazing cone variations. The milkshakes are fantastic! Conveniently located in beautiful Lee Tung Street, in Wan Chai.
Great ice cream!

The second and last time I will ever be having E&B - the first time being at their location in Kimberly TST. 
Overly sweet, too melty/temperature is too high, and costly for this forgettable ice cream.

The ice cream cones are  spectacular. I tried the fruit loop infused cones and was epic. There are a wide range of quite ice cream flavours; ranging for the standard flavours to a few special ones. Worth a try if you are around. Expect to pay around $60 for an ice cream. They also have milkshakes and smoothies.

reviews.text:
Barman has got talent, nice atmosphere here.
But waiters are not so helpful. Anyway it's a very nice adress with very good choice in Lee Tung Avenue. Just go.

Not impressed. Servers appear to be doing you a favour by serving you. Sat downstairs in the bar and had some snacks as they don't serve dinner until 6.30pm. Tried to order off the dinner menu at 6.30 only to be told that dinner is only served upstairs.

Moved upstairs only to find out that some of our choices off the menu were not available 😥
I love the unusual design concept of the shops. Large range of whiskey. Great bar tender the drinks are great.
Real Japanese bar near to our hotel. Amazing choice of Japanese whisky and cocktails. Friendly staff. We enjoyed our stay there. Will come back next time.

Amazingly flavorful food, decor is incredible. Went as a group of 15, staff helpfully put together a reasonable and fabulous menu. Great fusion food. 

Has a section overlooking Lee tung Avenue. Very helpful and friendly staff.

reviews.text: 半年前，經常光顧這家餐廳，藝術的裝潢、藤燈的輕鬆，讓人一再回購，吃過或許有五、六、七、八、九此，午餐餐點價錢一直維持在$98到$148不等。年初懷疑易手後，餐點風格大變，從巴西風走到今天的混搭風，混搭到不知是什麼，餐點也劃一是$138（另加一），增加了沙拉與餐飲，但仍無法彌補素食餐點超過百分之四十的加幅、肉餐點加價百分之二十五。原本餐牌那道好吃的醋蘋果、蒸蕃薯、沙拉菜配豆已然消失不見，換來是青瓜沙拉，略見誠意不足。

呢間舖由利東街開張至今都有留意，不過一直未有機會去試下。上年有一次想夜晚 walk-in 入去食點知話 full，心諗，今次 walk-in 都係一樣，不過都試下打電話去問問。點知打去話有位，仲要星期日晚添。

好了，入到去最吸引既係個環境，本身已經知道係好靚，咁我地成班人都諗住入去影相飲杯野咁。咁上到樓上見到完全無人，真係嚇左跳，最後成晚原來除左我地八人一枱外，就只有一枱三人黎過，同之前話 full 晒完全兩回事，心諗究竟係上次俾人包左場真依家再無人去呢？唔緊要，無人仲好方便影相。不過坐低後 d 真係覺得好唔自在，d waiter 一 d 笑容都無仲要好唔友善，好似覺得我地入黎唔幫襯咁。之後好快佢地就介紹 menu 有 d 乜食，然後仲建議話每人要食乜乜，好了，既然入得黎幫襯就預左，所以我地八人每人都叫左杯野飲，再叫三個小食。老實講野食味道ok，環境亦ok，但服務真係九流，全程全部人都黑口黑面，已問準你地可唔可以影相你地話ok，但又要望住晒驚整爛你d 野咁，行埋少少影相就即刻走埋黎好無禮貌咁話唔可以掂到牆，真係當我地搞破壞.. d 小食唔平，八個人食每人只係食幾啖，野飲還算ok, 最平既可樂係 $38, 預左.. 但最後每人埋單成 $200，真係無下次。唔係貴唔貴問題，係態度同服務勁差.. 可能因為我地唔係鬼佬？定覺得我地無錢畀？見你星期日晚都只有兩枱，真係諗唔到你地仲頂唔頂到...  (第一次打咁多字既comment.. 真心覺得呢間野狗眼看人低)
